dl.dd:
array, REQUIRED. minItems: 1; uniqueItems: true;
      each item matches
      <dot-separated-scope-name>.

string, OPTIONAL. Pattern:
      eng:<UUIDv4-lowerhex>;
      present when the token is scoped to an Engagement Object.

section.artwork:
effective = base_manifest.capabilities
for each active_overlay in applicable_overlays:
    effective = intersect(effective, active_overlay.constraints)
